
Overview of noun receiver

The noun receiver has 6 senses (first 4 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (4) receiver, receiving system -- (set that receives radio or tv signals)
2. (3) liquidator, receiver -- ((law) a person (usually appointed by a court of law) who liquidates assets or preserves them for the benefit of affected parties)
3. (3) telephone receiver, receiver -- (earphone that converts electrical signals into sounds)
4. (1) recipient, receiver -- (a person who receives something)
5. receiver -- (the tennis player who receives the serve)
6. receiver, pass receiver, pass catcher -- (a football player who catches (or is supposed to catch) a forward pass)
